Hey! I'm EK-BOT, created by <@363773759095701507>!
Here are some easy commands for you to learn that could help a lot!

**ek-help** - Sends you a list of commands!
**ek-ban [USER]** - Bans a certain user! Don't forget to mention the person where [USER] is
**ek-kick [USER]** - Same as above, but kicks them!
**ek-grouplink** - Supplies you with the roblox group link!
**ek-whois [USER]** - Displays limited info about a user
**ek-suggest [SUGGESTION]** - Suggests something to the bot creator, like a new feature.
**ek-support** - Graps attention of support staff!

**ANY ISSUES DM <@363773759095701507> OR DO ek-suggest!**
